snippet.title: Paper Dolls Original - Bringing Horror to Nintendo Switch eShop
snippet.description:
Paper Dolls Original is a terrifying horror experience that's coming to Nintendo Switch eShop on 19th September.

Immersive graphics and a unique Eastern vibe bring a terrifying mansion to life. Experience a finely-crafted soundtrack, combining chant with folk and rock music, as you delve deeper into the darkness.

Follow us on Twitter! https://twitter.com/CIRCLE_Ent
